code: @Override public void setup(int numberOfChannels) {     super.setup(numberOfChannels).     nextChannelToSendTo = ThreadLocalRandom.current().nextInt(numberOfChannels). }
@Override public int selectChannel(SerializationDelegate<StreamRecord<T>> record) {     nextChannelToSendTo = (nextChannelToSendTo + 1) % numberOfChannels.     return nextChannelToSendTo. }
